@page "/privacy-policy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy — PdfToolStack</PageTitle>

<div class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">

        <div class="legal-header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="legal-date">Last updated: April 11, 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-content">

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>
                    Welcome to PdfToolStack ("we," "our," or "us").
                    We are committed to protecting your personal
                    information and your right to privacy. This
                    Privacy Policy explains what data we collect,
                    why we collect it, and what rights you have
                    over your data when you use
                    <strong>PdfToolStack.com</strong>.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We do not run advertisements. We do not sell
                    your data. We do not use third-party analytics
                    or tracking cookies.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

                <h3>Files you upload</h3>
                <p>
                    PDF and other files you upload are processed
                    to perform the tool operation you requested
                    and returned to you. Files are stored
                    temporarily on Microsoft Azure Blob Storage
                    and are automatically and permanently deleted
                    within <strong>1 hour</strong>. We never
                    read, analyze, sell, or share the contents
                    of your documents.
                </p>

                <h3>Account information</h3>
                <p>
                    If you create an account, we collect your
                    email address and name via Auth0, our
                    authentication provider. Auth0 stores your
                    login credentials securely on their
                    infrastructure. We store your user ID in
                    our database to associate your subscription
                    and usage history with your account.
                </p>

                <h3>Subscription and billing data</h3>
                <p>
                    If you subscribe to Pro, your payment is
                    processed by Stripe. We never see or store
                    your credit card details. We store your
                    Stripe customer ID, subscription status,
                    and billing period in our database to
                    manage your subscription.
                </p>

                <h3>Download history</h3>
                <p>
                    For logged-in users, we store a record of
                    which tools you used, the file name, file
                    size, and timestamp. This is displayed in
                    your account dashboard and used to improve
                    our service. You can delete this data at
                    any time by deleting your account.
                </p>

                <h3>AI usage logs</h3>
                <p>
                    When you use AI-powered tools such as the
                    AI Contract Reviewer or Invoice Extractor,
                    we log your user ID, the tool used, token
                    count, and timestamp. We do not log the
                    content of your documents. These logs are
                    used to enforce fair usage limits.
                </p>

                <h3>Server logs</h3>
                <p>
                    Our servers automatically log standard
                    request data including IP address, browser
                    type, and pages visited. These logs are
                    retained for 30 days for security and
                    abuse prevention purposes and are then
                    automatically deleted.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>To process your PDF files and return results to you</li>
                    <li>To manage your account and subscription</li>
                    <li>To enforce usage limits and prevent abuse</li>
                    <li>To send transactional emails such as subscription confirmations</li>
                    <li>To improve and optimize our tools and services</li>
                    <li>To monitor for security threats and fraud</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    We do not use your data for advertising,
                    profiling, or any purpose not listed above.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p>
                    We use the following third-party services
                    to operate PdfToolStack:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Microsoft Azure</strong> —
                        Hosting, database, and file storage.
                        Data is processed in the West US 2
                        region (United States).
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Auth0</strong> —
                        Authentication and user account
                        management.
                        <a href="https://auth0.com/privacy"
                           target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                            Auth0 Privacy Policy
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Stripe</strong> —
                        Payment processing. We never see your
                        card details.
                        <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy"
                           target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                            Stripe Privacy Policy
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Anthropic Claude</strong> —
                        AI processing for AI-powered tools.
                        Document content sent to AI tools is
                        processed by Anthropic's API and is
                        not stored by Anthropic per their
                        API data usage policy.
                        <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy"
                           target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                            Anthropic Privacy Policy
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Resend</strong> —
                        Transactional email delivery.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>5. Data Residency</h2>
                <p>
                    PdfToolStack is hosted on Microsoft Azure
                    in the <strong>West US 2</strong> region
                    (United States). If you are located in the
                    European Union or United Kingdom, your data
                    is transferred to and processed in the
                    United States. This transfer is made on the
                    basis of our legitimate interests in
                    providing you with our service and is
                    subject to appropriate safeguards.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
                <p>
                    We use only essential cookies and browser
                    local storage. We do not use advertising,
                    tracking, or analytics cookies.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>pdftoolstack-cookie-consent</strong>
                        — Stores your cookie preference.
                        Essential. Expires after 1 year.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>PdfToolStack-theme</strong>
                        — Stores your light/dark mode
                        preference. Essential. Expires after
                        1 year.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Auth0 session cookies</strong>
                        — Required for authentication.
                        Essential. Session duration.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    See our <a href="/cookie-policy">
                        Cookie Policy
                    </a> for full details.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Uploaded files</strong> —
                        Deleted within 1 hour of processing
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Server logs</strong> —
                        Deleted after 30 days
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Account data</strong> —
                        Retained until you delete your account
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Subscription records</strong>
                        — Retained for 7 years for tax and
                        legal compliance, even after account
                        deletion
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>8. Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
                <p>
                    Depending on your location, you have the
                    following rights regarding your personal data:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Right of access</strong> —
                        Request a copy of the data we hold
                        about you
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Right to erasure</strong> —
                        Delete your account and all associated
                        data via your
                        <a href="/account">Account page</a>
                        or by contacting us
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Right to portability</strong>
                        — Request your data in a portable format
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Right to object</strong> —
                        Object to processing of your data
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Right to lodge a complaint</strong>
                        — With your local data protection
                        authority
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    To exercise any of these rights, visit your
                    <a href="/account">Account page</a> or
                    contact us at
                    <a href="mailto:privacy@pdftoolstack.com">
                        privacy@pdftoolstack.com
                    </a>.
                    We will respond within 30 days.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
                <p>
                    PdfToolStack is not directed at children
                    under the age of 13. We do not knowingly
                    collect personal information from children.
                    If you believe a child has provided us with
                    personal information, please contact us
                    immediately at
                    <a href="mailto:privacy@pdftoolstack.com">
                        privacy@pdftoolstack.com
                    </a>.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>
                    We may update this Privacy Policy from time
                    to time. We will notify you of material
                    changes by posting the new policy on this
                    page and updating the "Last updated" date.
                    Your continued use of our service after
                    changes constitutes acceptance of the
                    updated policy.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions about this Privacy
                    Policy or your data, please contact us:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Email:
                        <a href="mailto:privacy@pdftoolstack.com">
                            privacy@pdftoolstack.com
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Data deletion:
                        <a href="/account/delete">
                            pdftoolstack.com/account/delete
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>